862
01:16:20,830 --> 01:16:22,080
Sauce?

863
01:16:22,248 --> 01:16:24,207
Yeah, sauce, you know, sauce.

864
01:16:24,375 --> 01:16:27,252
- Is that code?
- No, it's not code.

865
01:16:27,420 --> 01:16:29,296
- You just said you're a
real Italian, right? - Si.

866
01:16:29,463 --> 01:16:32,799
