875
01:17:01,370 --> 01:17:03,955
Hello. I am Guido.

876
01:17:04,123 --> 01:17:05,624
Hi, Guido,
this will only take a second.

877
01:17:05,791 --> 01:17:06,791
No, no!

878
01:17:06,959 --> 01:17:09,836
- Please take all the time you want.
- Who's Guido?

879
01:17:10,004 --> 01:17:12,339
No, no, no.

880
01:17:12,506 --> 01:17:17,052
So, this is my mama's favorite
reduction sauce.

881
01:17:17,219 --> 01:17:22,390
