to take care of her.

886
01:17:40,284 --> 01:17:41,576
What else, Guido?

887
01:17:43,204 --> 01:17:48,208
Heat the olive oil,
crush the garlic.

888
01:17:48,376 --> 01:17:50,877
Then you peel the tomatoes.

889
01:17:51,045 --> 01:17:53,338
After ten minutes, no more,

890
01:17:53,506 --> 01:17:56,633
add capers and parsley.

891
01:17:56,801 --> 01:18:00,845
And my mama's secret
is a cup of red wine

892
01:18:01,013 --> 01:18:03,098
and a teaspoon of sugar.

893
01:18:04,642 --> 01:18:07,894
Boy, that Guido's a real mama's boy, huh?

894
01:18:08,062 --> 01:18:11,147
I think it's sweet that he
loves his mother. Thanks, Ethan.

895
01:18:11,315 --> 01:18:15,193
- Remember, don't get home too early.
- OK.

896
01:18:16,362 --> 01:18:18,613
No, wait!

897
01:18:18,781 --> 01:18:21,116
Oh, please call her back.

898
01:18:21,283 --> 01:18:25,578
I wanted to give her my mama's
favorite recipe for cannoli.

