902
01:18:36,125 --> 01:18:37,875
That's two hours.

903
01:18:38,043 --> 01:18:40,419
You cut this guy loose
in two hours.

904
01:18:40,587 --> 01:18:43,881
Guido, remind me where you're going
after this kid lets you go.

905
01:18:44,049 --> 01:18:47,051
I'm going back home
to live with Mama!

906
01:19:06,947 --> 01:19:08,114
You're late.

907
01:19:09,950 --> 01:19:11,742
I'm in the middle
of a training session.

908
01:19:12,452 --> 01:19:16,164
Yeah, I... I can see that.

909
01:19:21,253 --> 01:19:22,628
