943
01:22:47,207 --> 01:22:48,624
It is a girl.

944
01:22:59,594 --> 01:23:02,346
Before the baby leaves the house
for the first time,

945
01:23:02,514 --> 01:23:07,017
it is our custom to have
the family offer a blessing.

946
01:23:08,770 --> 01:23:11,480
